# Admin API (required for Generate + QR Library). Never commit real secrets.
VITE_ADMIN_API_SECRET=
# Optional; must match worker ADMIN_API_SECRET_HEADER (default X-Admin-Key)
# VITE_ADMIN_API_SECRET_HEADER=X-Admin-Key

# Leave empty to use same-origin /api (Vite dev proxies to wrangler — see vite.config.ts).
# Or set to your deployed worker origin, e.g. https://your-worker.workers.dev
# VITE_API_BASE_URL=

# Optional: override wrangler dev URL for the Vite proxy (default http://127.0.0.1:8787)
# VITE_DEV_WORKER_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8787
